headline: Abbott's FreeStyle Libre® 2 Now Reimbursed for Children and Adults Living with Diabetes in Alberta
summary: Abbott (NYSE: ABT) today announced that the Government of Alberta has added Abbott's FreeStyle Libre 2* flash glucose monitoring system to the Alberta Drug Benefit List.

headline: Abbott Announces First-in-World Leadless Pacing Procedures in the Left Bundle Branch Area of the Heart
summary: Abbott (NYSE: ABT) today announced the successful completion of the world's first in-human leadless left bundle branch area pacing (LBBAP) procedures using the company's investigational AVEIR™ Conduction System Pacing (CSP) leadless pacemaker system, as part of a feasibility study.
